30643123741319511643.Text: I'm told that Addhiranirr is hiding because a Census and Excise agent is in the area. She's probably down in the underworks.

148792839765926703.Text: Addhiranirr will be hiding in the underworks while the Census and Excise agent is in the area.

2036832174183455127.Text: Addhiranirr was too concerned about the Census and Excise agent to answer questions for the Spymaster. Maybe I can do something to get rid of him.

2719613612229508884.Text: When I told the Census and Excise agent that Addhiranirr took a gondola to the mainland, he said he was heading back to the mainland anyway, and would look for her there. Maybe Addhiranirr will be grateful that I've gotten rid of him for her.

103936328262522564.Text: Addhiranirr was pleased that I'd taken care of the Census and Excise agent she'd been worrying about, and now she's ready to answer my questions on the Nerevarine cult and the Sixth House cult.

5594065291889243.Text: Addhiranirr says that some smugglers are now working for the Sixth House, but Addhiranirr couldn't find out what they are smuggling. Addhiranirr thought it was strange that smugglers who usually brag about their smuggling are suddenly being very quiet about what they smuggle for the Sixth House. I wonder what is being smuggled, and why it is such a big secret. I think this is the sort of thing Caius Cosades is looking for.

6134106522752623066.Text: When I told the Census and Excise agent to look for Addhiranirr in the underworks, he was pleased. He didn't seem in a hurry to do anything, though. I wonder how Addhiranirr will feel about what I've done.

16668297552055419639.Text: Addhiranirr was angry that I'd told the Census and Excise agent where to find her. Now it's going to be very hard to persuade her to answer my questions on the Nerevarine cult and the Sixth House cult.

31000343144618781.Text: I finally managed to persuade Addhiranirr to answer my questions on the Nerevarine cult and the Sixth House cult.
